reviewText: I have a 1 and a 2 year old.  Both children absolutely adore this video.  Can't believe it's not more readily available in the US, it's all across Europe as a #1 kiddie nighttime favourite.
This movies is great for young kids! My son really loves it and watches it before he sleeps and when he wakes up! Its annoying to me but this is what will keep him entertained!
